productReviews.reviewText: I saw one of these in Sao Tome and Principe and I bought one.
It only works when I'm Martinique.
The box this comes in is 3 yard by 6 light-year and weights 15 gram!!!
My co-worker Aurthur has one of these. He says it looks white.
My neighbor Forest has one of these. She works as a gardener and she says it looks nude.
